summary: Haha that time of year again where I look back on all of my drawings and tbh this time I think I got some months confused but oh...
caption:
Haha that time of year again where I look back on all of my drawings and tbh this time I think I got some months confused but oh well! Ngl I feel like I’ve improved a lot this year and I’ve never felt so happy about my art in a long time.

This year was a good art year for me and I hope next year will be too (especially since my newest project is Craven which I am so excited for!) 

Thank you for the support and I can’t wait for what I’ll create next year!
